Louisiana's 64 parishes, FIPS codes, and region designations according to different state agencies and organizations (long format).

Source: R/data.R
parishes_long.Rd

Louisiana's 64 parishes, FIPS codes, and region designations according to different state agencies and organizations (long format).

Usage

parishes_long

Format

A data frame with 393 rows and 8 columns:

FIPS

Parish FIPS code

parish, parish_full

Parish name with & without "Parish"

name

Full parish name including "Parish, Louisiana"

metro_BLS

"Metropolitan area" or "Nonmetropolitan area" as designated by BLS

org

Name of agency or organization for region designation

region_number

Region numeric ID

region_name

Region name ID

Source

LAPDD, DCFS, One Acadiana, LWC, BLS, LDH, OJJ
